-*- outline -*-

* Non-LUA required software
---------------------------
- smc (http://smc.sourceforge.net)

- graphviz

(- ev-dev)


* LUA requirements
------------------
- lua 5.1+ with C dev header

- luasocket (http://w3.impa.br/~diego/software/luasocket/) (only C hard
  dependency)

- vstruct (https://github.com/ToxicFrog/vstruct)

if unittests should be runnable
- busted (http://olivinelabs.com/busted/)
(- md5 - needed for 'speed' / 'fun' development)


* Installation
--------------

